      "correct_option_id": "1",
      "explanation": "$\\sin^{-1}\\!\\left(-\\dfrac{1}{4}\\right)=\\alpha$ ⇒ $\\sin\\alpha=-\\dfrac{1}{4}$ ($\\alpha$는 4사분면각).\n$\\cos\\alpha=\\dfrac{\\sqrt{15}}{4}$.\n또는 $\\cos$는 우함수: $\\cos\\!\\left(-\\sin^{-1}\\dfrac{1}{4}\\right)=\\cos\\!\\left(\\sin^{-1}\\dfrac{1}{4}\\right)=\\dfrac{\\sqrt{15}}{4}$.",
      "tags": ["daily","미분학","역삼각함수","단답형"]
